INSERT INTO `projects` VALUES (1,'Surgery for Disabled','Jack’s Journey Jack, a vibrant and determined individual, has always been an inspiration to those around him. Despite his disability, he has never let it define him or limit his dreams. Recently, he was presented with a glimmer of hope - a surgical procedure that could potentially enable him to walk again. This surgery, although complex, has been successful in numerous cases, giving individuals with disabilities a new lease on life.\n\nThe Power of Perseverance In anticipation of the surgery, Jack has been tirelessly working out, strengthening his body and spirit for the challenges ahead. His unwavering commitment is a testament to his resilience and determination. Every bead of sweat brings him one step closer to his dream of walking again. His journey is a powerful reminder that our limitations are often self-imposed, and with the right mindset, we can overcome any obstacle.\n\nA Call for Support However, this journey is not one that Jack can embark on alone. The surgery, while promising, comes with significant costs. Jack is reaching out to friends, family, and kind-hearted strangers to help make this dream a reality. Any contribution, no matter how small, brings him one step closer to his goal. It’s more than just a surgery; it’s a chance for Jack to reclaim his independence and live life to the fullest. Let’s stand with Jack and help him take this crucial step towards a brighter future.','With a new hope for being able to walk again,Jack is not missing a workout and is asking for your help to do the Surgery.','wheelchair person.jpg',20000.00,19650.00,48,23,1,'2024-05-05 14:28:45','disability',1,NULL),(2,'Sustainable Fashion Line','Sustainable Fashion, Redefined We are thrilled to introduce our new sustainable fashion line, a perfect blend of style and eco-friendliness. This innovative collection is not just about making a fashion statement, but also about making a commitment to our planet. Crafted with responsibly sourced materials and ethical manufacturing processes, each piece embodies our dedication to sustainability, without compromising on style.\n\nStyle Meets Sustainability Our new line challenges the notion that fashion and sustainability are mutually exclusive. Each garment is designed with an eye for trend, ensuring you don’t have to choose between looking good and doing good. From chic dresses to versatile separates, the collection offers a range of options that cater to diverse tastes, all while reducing environmental impact.\n\nFashion for a Better Future By choosing our sustainable fashion line, you’re not just updating your wardrobe - you’re contributing to a more sustainable future. Each purchase helps reduce waste, lower carbon emissions, and promote ethical labor practices. It’s more than just fashion; it’s a movement towards a more conscious and sustainable way of life. Join us in making a difference, one stylish outfit at a time.','Introducing a new sustainable fashion line that combines style and eco-friendliness while saving the planet.','../img/Sustainable Fashion Line img.jpeg',50000.00,28000.00,620,30,1,'2024-05-05 16:09:28','environment',1,NULL),(13,'Boys in need!!','Ahmad, Ali, and Mohammad are three ambitious young men with a shared dream of completing their master\'s degrees in computer science at the AUB university. Having excelled in their undergraduate studies, they are determined to further their education and contribute to the ever-evolving field of technology. However, the financial burden of higher education is a significant challenge for them, and they have turned to crowdfunding as a means to overcome this obstacle.\n\nThe trio has a clear vision of how advanced knowledge in computer science can open doors to innovative opportunities. Ahmad, with his keen interest in artificial intelligence, aims to develop smart solutions that can improve daily life. Ali, passionate about cybersecurity, wants to create safer online environments. Mohammad, who excels in software development, dreams of building applications that can transform industries. Together, they believe that their diverse skills and collective efforts will make a substantial impact.\n\nBy launching their crowdfunding campaign, Ahmad, Ali, and Mohammad hope to garner support from a global community that values education and innovation. They are committed to keeping their backers updated with their progress and sharing their academic and project achievements. With the funds raised, they plan to cover tuition fees, purchase essential resources, and dedicate time to their research and projects. Through this initiative, they not only seek financial assistance but also aim to inspire others to pursue their educational goals despite financial challenges.','Three ambitious friends, Ahmad, Ali, and Mohammad, are crowdfunding their master\'s degrees in computer science at the AUB university to overcome financial barriers and pursue their dreams of innovating in artificial intelligence, cybersecurity, and software development.','d2ea0d49-12af-11ef-bd38-a0595001c18c-WIN_20240515_14_38_21_Pro_2.jpg',300000.00,290250.00,6,60,6,'2024-05-15 09:55:40','education',1,NULL),(15,'Sarah Lees\'s Science Fair Project','Sarah Lee, an enthusiastic sophomore at Central Valley High School, is deeply passionate about robotics. She is eager to participate in the upcoming science fair, where she plans to showcase her skills by presenting a line-following robot. However, to bring her project to life, Sarah requires financial assistance to acquire the necessary materials and components for building the robot.\r\n\r\n  Driven by her fervent interest in robotics, Sarah envisions her project as not only a personal endeavor but also as a potential avenue to inspire her peers and foster a love for STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering, and Mathematics) subjects within her school community. With the right support, Sarah believes her project could not only excel in the science fair but also serve as a testament to the power of determination and innovation among young students.\r\n\r\n  Your contribution to Sarah\'s fundraising campaign will not only provide her with the means to purchase essential components such as sensors, microcontrollers, and motors but also enable her to explore her creativity and problem-solving skills as she navigates the complexities of robotics design and implementation.\r\n\r\n  By supporting Sarah\'s endeavor, you\'re not just helping her build a robot; you\'re investing in the potential of a budding young scientist and empowering her to pursue her passion for robotics and technology. Together, we can help Sarah bring her vision to fruition and make a meaningful impact in the world of STEM education.','Passionate about robotics, sophomore Sarah Lee needs financial assistance to build a line-following robot for the science fair and inspire her peers to pursue STEM. ','981bd8d7-15fc-11ef-b5b1-a0595001c18c-msrobotics-12.jpg',300.00,50.00,1,30,8,'2024-05-19 16:24:46','education',1,'981c271a-15fc-11ef-a780-a0595001c18c-How_to_build_a_robot_in_one_minute.mp4'),(17,'Smart Garden System','Introducing a revolutionary Smart Garden System that transforms traditional gardening into an effortless and efficient experience. This cutting-edge system is designed to take the guesswork out of plant care by utilizing advanced sensors and automated technology. It monitors soil moisture, sunlight, and temperature in real-time, ensuring that plants receive the optimal conditions they need to thrive. Gardeners no longer have to worry about overwatering or neglecting their plants, as the Smart Garden System provides precise care instructions and automated watering schedules.\r\n\r\nThe Smart Garden System is not just about automation; it also empowers gardeners with valuable insights and data. Through a user-friendly mobile app, users can track the health and growth of their plants, receive alerts for potential issues, and access a wealth of gardening tips and information. This connectivity allows gardeners to make informed decisions and adjustments, fostering a more engaging and educational gardening experience. Whether you are a novice or an experienced gardener, this system adapts to your needs and helps you cultivate a flourishing garden.\r\n\r\nEfficiency is at the heart of the Smart Garden System. By optimizing water usage and reducing the need for manual intervention, it conserves resources and promotes sustainable gardening practices. This system is perfect for busy individuals who love gardening but struggle to find the time for daily upkeep. With its sleek design and seamless integration into any garden setting, the Smart Garden System revolutionizes how we interact with nature, making it easier than ever to enjoy the benefits of a thriving garden with minimal effort.','The Smart Garden System revolutionizes gardening by automating plant care, providing data-driven insights, and promoting sustainable practices for both novice and experienced gardeners. \n','74878869-1613-11ef-a299-a0595001c18c-Smart_Garden_System_img.jpeg',75000.00,42500.00,785,45,7,'2024-05-19 19:08:18','environment',1,''),(18,'Heart Surgery for Amelia Jones','Amelia’s Journey Amelia Jones, a cherished grandmother and a pillar of strength in her family, is facing a significant health challenge. She requires a heart surgery that holds the promise of greatly improving her quality of life. This surgery, while necessary, is a major procedure that comes with substantial costs. It’s a hurdle, but with the support of her loved ones and the wider community, it’s one that Amelia is ready to overcome.\r\n\r\nThe Power of Community In times like these, the power of community becomes evident. We’re rallying together to raise funds to help cover the costs of Amelia’s heart surgery. Every contribution, no matter how small, brings us one step closer to reaching our goal. It’s more than just a donation; it’s a testament to the power of collective action and the profound impact we can have when we support one another.\r\n\r\nA Call for Support We invite you to join us in supporting Amelia in this critical phase of her life. Your contribution will not only help cover the costs of the surgery but also provide Amelia with the emotional support and strength she needs during this time. It’s more than just a medical procedure; it’s about giving Amelia the chance to enjoy her life to the fullest with her grandchildren. Let’s come together for Amelia and show her that she’s not alone in this journey.','The community is rallying together to raise funds for Amelia Jones\'s heart surgery, providing financial and emotional support to help her overcome this health challenge and enjoy life with her grandchildren. \n','64b046cc-161c-11ef-8413-a0595001c18c-grandma-pexels-photo-432722-820x500.jpeg',50000.00,12345.00,57,15,2,'2024-05-19 19:27:11','health',1,''),(19,'Masters Degree Persuit','Nawal’s Aspirations Nawal, a passionate and ambitious individual, is on a journey to fulfill her dreams. She has set her sights on pursuing a master’s degree in Computer Science at the American University of Beirut (AUB), renowned globally for its excellence in this field. This pursuit is not just about academic advancement, but a testament to Nawal’s determination to push boundaries and make a significant impact in the world of technology.\r\n\r\nThe Path Ahead The road to achieving this dream is filled with challenges and opportunities. Nawal is looking forward to immersing herself in advanced studies, exploring the latest in artificial intelligence, data science, and cybersecurity. She is eager to learn from distinguished faculty and collaborate with like-minded peers at AUB, a university known for fostering innovation and critical thinking.\r\n\r\nA Call for Support As Nawal embarks on this exciting journey, she appreciates the support and encouragement from her community. This pursuit is not just about Nawal’s personal growth, but also about contributing to the broader scientific community and inspiring other aspiring technologists. Let’s stand with Nawal as she takes this significant step towards achieving her dreams, shaping the future of technology, and making a difference in the world.','Passionate and ambitious, Nawal is pursuing a master\'s degree in Computer Science at the American University of Beirut to push boundaries in technology and make a significant impact on the world. \n','e228321c-161c-11ef-ae54-a0595001c18c-graduate.avif',40000.00,19680.00,362,90,2,'2024-05-19 19:27:11','education',1,''),(20,'test_proj','Popular Categories\nHealth and Medical Expenses\nFundraising in this category supports individuals or organizations facing high medical costs, including medical treatments, surgeries, medications, or medical equipment.\n\nEducation\nFunds raised in this category support educational initiatives, including scholarships, school supplies, building schools, or providing access to quality education for underprivileged individuals.\n\nDisability Rights\nThis category focuses on fundraising for organizations and initiatives that support individuals with disabilities, advocating for their rights, accessibility, and inclusion in society.\n\nEnvironmental Conservation\nFunds raised here go towards projects and organizations dedicated to preserving and protecting the environment, including conservation efforts, wildlife protection, sustainable practices, and combating climate change','Popular fundraising categories encompass vital areas like healthcare, education, disability rights, and environmental conservation, aiming to improve the well-being of individuals and the planet. \n','732cf1b4-161d-11ef-a579-a0595001c18c-051d8660-0c69-11ef-a092-a0595001c18c-4cccfdb90c3e88ab6fec86a4cf9faa99.jpg',10000.00,0.00,0,50,2,'2024-05-19 19:27:11','disability',0,'');
